<link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r=
1320445320"><div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">=
Main article: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Riemann_integral" ti=
tle=3D"Riemann integral">Riemann integral</a></div>
<p>The Riemann integral is defined in terms of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/Riemann_sum" title=3D"Riemann sum">Riemann sums</a> of functio=
ns with respect to <i>tagged partitions</i> of an interval.<sup id=3D"cite_=
ref-22" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integr=
al#cite_note-22"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>21<span class=3D"cite=
-bracket">]</span></a></sup> A tagged partition of a <a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/Closed_interval" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Closed i=
nterval">closed interval</a> <span class=3D"texhtml">[<i>a</i>, <i>b</i>]</=
span> on the real line is a finite sequence
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e a=3Dx_{0}\leq t_{1}\leq x_{1}\leq t_{2}\leq x_{2}\leq \cdots \leq x_{n-1}=
\leq t_{n}\leq x_{n}=3Db.\,\!}">
  <semantics>
