^{n}f(t_{i})\,\Delta _{i};}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/76e9ff892e308950da2bbe3f2ac7b0a51356c6ce" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
