">volume</a> of the region between the surface defined by the function and =
the plane that contains its domain.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-40" class=3D"referen=
ce"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integral#cite_note-40"><span c=
lass=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>39<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></=
