er/svg/47136aad860d145f75f3eed3022df827cee94d7a" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.764ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle B}"=
></span> is:<sup id=3D"cite_ref-54" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://=
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integral#cite_note-54"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[=
</span>53<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
